    <Fragment slot="content">
        <h1 class="text-3xl text-socialswingblue dark:text-gray-300">Jesse Lopez</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-socialswingblue dark:text-gray-300">
            Less of a Unicorn; More of a Mushroom
        </br>
            ~ADHD Empowered + Neurologically Evolving~
        </br>
        WHAT I DO:
        </br>
        I teach the Body Language of West Coast Swing. I provide Adventurers, Thinkers and Creatives an Inclusive and Consent focused dance environment where they can pursue joy, development, and movement. I am actively driving to change the world of WCS education by reestablishing Physical Connection to oneself and one’s partner on the dance floor with the goal of helping our kinetic human computers reconnect to the joy of community, movement and music. I pursue my passion for the Kinetic Dance Languages around the world, traveling as an Instructor, Judge and Competitor from Coast to Coast across the States and around the World. If your dance life is missing improvisation, passion, or efficiency, send me a DM and let’s talk about how we can evolve your dance. 
        </br>
        WHY I DO IT։
        </br>
        Dancing is my safe space and my purest form of expression. Sharing the love of swing dancing with my home KC and abroad communities fulfills my Ikigai, and I look forward to people experiencing the environmental positivity of the WCS social dance floor.
        </p>
        
    </Fragment>
