            <p class="text-1xl text-socialswingblue dark:text-gray-300">I've been dancing since I was 8 years old. I grew up doing ballet and had the opportunity to perform roles such as Clara, Dewdrop, and Lead Swan with Ballet Midwest in Topeka. In high school and college, I taught ballet classes and danced with a local touring group called Cleargold. I first tried swing dancing in high school and started partner dancing more regularly in college, in a variety of styles including east coast swing, lindy hop, Charleston, salsa, and bachata. I started dancing west coast swing in 2019, and it quickly became my favorite style. I love growing in my own dance and helping others do the same.</p>
